(ns farsund.core
  (:require [farsund.init]
            [goog.events :as events]
            [goog.history.EventType :as HistoryEventType]
            [reagent.core :as r]
            [re-frame.core :as rf]
            [taoensso.timbre :as timbre]
            [farsund.ui.core :as ui]
            )
  (:import goog.History))


(defn mount-components []
  (timbre/info "components mounted!")
  (r/render [#'ui/main-page] (.getElementById js/document "app")))


(defn init []
  (timbre/set-level! :debug)
  (timbre/debug :init!)
  (rf/dispatch-sync [:farsund/boot])
  (rf/clear-subscription-cache!)
  (mount-components))

(init)
